{"id":99,"parent_id":95,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":99,"title":"Acts 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"Acts","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","Peter and John are arrested and brought before the council—Peter testifies that salvation comes because of Christ—The Sadducees strive to silence Peter and John—The Saints glory in the testimony of Jesus—They have all things in common."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.1","order":"03.07.004.12211"},["b","1"],"And as they spake unto the people, the priests, and the captain of the temple, and the Sadducees, came upon them,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.2","order":"03.07.004.12212"},["b","2"],"Being grieved that they taught the people, and preached through Jesus the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"resurrection"],"from the dead."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.3","order":"03.07.004.12213"},["b","3"],"And they laid hands on them, and put",["i","them"],"in hold unto the next day: for it was now eventide."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.4","order":"03.07.004.12214"},["b","4"],"Howbeit many of them which heard the word believed; and the number of the men was about",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"five"],"thousand."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.5","order":"03.07.004.12215"},["b","5"],"¶And it came to pass on the morrow, that their rulers, and elders, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"scribes"],","],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.6","order":"03.07.004.12216"},["b","6"],"And Annas the high priest, and Caiaphas, and John, and Alexander, and as many as were of the kindred of the high",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"priest"],", were gathered together at Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.7","order":"03.07.004.12217"},["b","7"],"And when they had set them in the midst, they asked, By what",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"power"],", or by what",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"name"],", have ye done this?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.8","order":"03.07.004.12218"},["b","8"],"Then Peter, filled with the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Holy Ghost"],", said unto them, Ye rulers of the people, and elders of Israel,"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.9","order":"03.07.004.12219"},["b","9"],"If we this day be examined of the good deed done to the impotent man, by what means he is made whole;"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.10","order":"03.07.004.12220"},["b","10"],"Be it known unto you all, and to all the people of Israel, that by the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"name"],"of Jesus Christ of Nazareth, whom ye crucified, whom God raised from the dead,",["i","even"],"by him doth this man stand here before you whole."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.11","order":"03.07.004.12221"},["b","11"],"This is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"stone"],"which was set at nought of you builders, which is become the head of the corner."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.12","order":"03.07.004.12222"},["b","12"],"Neither is there",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"salvation"],"in any other: for there is none other",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"name"],"under heaven given among men, whereby we must be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"saved"],"."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.13","order":"03.07.004.12223"},["b","13"],"¶Now when they saw the boldness of Peter and John, and perceived that they were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"unlearned"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"ignorant"],"men, they marvelled; and they took knowledge of them, that they had been with Jesus."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.14","order":"03.07.004.12224"},["b","14"],"And beholding the man which was healed standing with them, they could say nothing against it."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.15","order":"03.07.004.12225"},["b","15"],"But when they had commanded them to go aside out of the council, they conferred among themselves,"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.16","order":"03.07.004.12226"},["b","16"],"Saying, What shall we do to these men? for that indeed a notable",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"miracle"],"hath been done by them",["i","is"],"manifest to all them that dwell in Jerusalem; and we cannot deny",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.17","order":"03.07.004.12227"},["b","17"],"But that it spread no further among the people, let us straitly threaten them, that they speak henceforth to no man in this name."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.18","order":"03.07.004.12228"},["b","18"],"And they called them, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"commanded"],"them not to speak at all nor teach in the name of Jesus."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.19","order":"03.07.004.12229"},["b","19"],"But Peter and John answered and said unto them, Whether it be right in the sight of God to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"hearken"],"unto you more than unto God, judge ye."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.20","order":"03.07.004.12230"},["b","20"],"For we cannot but",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"speak"],"the things which we have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"seen"],"and heard."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.21","order":"03.07.004.12231"},["b","21"],"So when they had further threatened them, they let them go, finding nothing how they might punish them, because of the people: for all",["i","men"],"glorified God for that which was done."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.22","order":"03.07.004.12232"},["b","22"],"For the man was above forty years old, on whom this miracle of healing was shewed."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.23","order":"03.07.004.12233"},["b","23"],"¶And being let go, they went to their own company, and reported all that the chief priests and elders had said unto them."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.24","order":"03.07.004.12234"},["b","24"],"And when they heard that, they lifted up their voice to God with one accord, and said, Lord, thou",["i","art"],"God, which hast made heaven, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"earth"],", and the sea, and all that in them is:"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.25","order":"03.07.004.12235"},["b","25"],"Who by the mouth of thy servant David hast said, Why did the heathen rage, and the people imagine vain things?"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.26","order":"03.07.004.12236"},["b","26"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"kings"],"of the earth stood up, and the rulers were gathered together against the Lord, and against his Christ."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.27","order":"03.07.004.12237"},["b","27"],"For of a truth against thy holy child Jesus, whom thou hast",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"anointed"],", both Herod, and Pontius Pilate, with the Gentiles, and the people of Israel, were gathered together,"],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.28","order":"03.07.004.12238"},["b","28"],"For to do whatsoever thy hand and thy counsel determined before to be done."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.29","order":"03.07.004.12239"},["b","29"],"And now, Lord, behold their threatenings: and grant unto thy servants, that with all boldness they may speak thy word,"],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.30","order":"03.07.004.12240"},["b","30"],"By stretching forth thine hand to heal; and that signs and wonders may be done by the name of thy holy child Jesus."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.31","order":"03.07.004.12241"},["b","31"],"¶And when they had prayed, the place was shaken where they were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"assembled"],"together; and they were all filled with the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_31b"},"Holy Ghost"],", and they spake the word of God with boldness."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.32","order":"03.07.004.12242"},["b","32"],"And the multitude of them that believed were of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"one"],"heart and of one soul: neither said any",["i","of them"],"that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_32b"},"ought"],"of the things which he",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_32c"},"possessed"],"was his own; but they had all things",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_32d"},"common"],"."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.33","order":"03.07.004.12243"},["b","33"],"And with great power gave the apostles",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"witness"],"of the resurrection of the Lord Jesus: and great",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_33b"},"grace"],"was upon them all."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.34","order":"03.07.004.12244"},["b","34"],"Neither was there any among them that lacked: for as many as were possessors of lands or houses",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"sold"],"them, and brought the prices of the things that were sold,"],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.35","order":"03.07.004.12245"},["b","35"],"And laid",["i","them"],"down at the apostles’ feet: and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_35a"},"distribution"],"was made unto every man according as he had",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_35b"},"need"],"."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.36","order":"03.07.004.12246"},["b","36"],"And Joses, who by the apostles was surnamed",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_36a"},"Barnabas"],", (which is, being interpreted, The son of consolation,) a Levite,",["i","and"],"of the country of Cyprus,"],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.37","order":"03.07.004.12247"},["b","37"],"Having land, sold",["i","it,"],"and brought the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_37a"},"money"],", and laid",["i","it"],"at the apostles’ feet."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.2a","order":"03.07.004.12248"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.8"},"Acts 23:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.4a","order":"03.07.004.12250"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/2.41"},"Acts 2:41"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.5a","order":"03.07.004.12252"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scribe"},"TG Scribe"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.6a","order":"03.07.004.12254"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priestcraft"},"TG Priestcraft"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.7a","order":"03.07.004.12256"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-power-of"},"TG Priesthood, Power of"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.7b","order":"03.07.004.12258"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/name"},"TG Name"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.8a","order":"03.07.004.12260"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/teaching-with-the-spirit"},"TG Teaching with the Spirit"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.10a","order":"03.07.004.12262"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.6"},"Acts 3:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.11a","order":"03.07.004.12264"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cornerstone"},"TG Cornerstone"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/rock"},"Rock"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.12a","order":"03.07.004.12266"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/gospel"},"TG Gospel"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.12b","order":"03.07.004.12268"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/9.10"},"Ps. 9:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.4"},"Hosea 13:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-jn/2.12"},"1 Jn. 2:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/25.20"},"2 Ne. 25:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.8"},"Mosiah 4:8"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-taking-the-name-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Taking the Name of"],"."],["div",{"id":"12c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.12c","order":"03.07.004.12270"},["b","12c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"},"TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-savior"},"Jesus Christ, Savior"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/salvation"},"Salvation"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/salvation-plan-of"},"Salvation, Plan of"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.13a","order":"03.07.004.12272"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.19"},"D&C 1:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.13"},"35:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.13b","order":"03.07.004.12274"},["b","13b"],["span.small","GR"],"ordinary, plain."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.16a","order":"03.07.004.12276"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.9.6-9"},"Acts 3:9 (6–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.18a","order":"03.07.004.12278"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/5.28.27-28"},"Acts 5:28 (27–28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.19a","order":"03.07.004.12280"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/3.7"},"D&C 3:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.20a","order":"03.07.004.12282"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.9"},"Jer. 20:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/3.8"},"Amos 3:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.20b","order":"03.07.004.12284"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/witness"},"TG Witness"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.24a","order":"03.07.004.12286"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/14.9"},"D&C 14:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.26a","order":"03.07.004.12288"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/2.2.1-2"},"Ps. 2:2 (1–2)"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.27a","order":"03.07.004.12290"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/anointing"},"TG Anointing"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-authority-of"},"Jesus Christ, Authority of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-messiah"},"Jesus Christ, Messiah"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.31a","order":"03.07.004.12292"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/assembly-for-worship"},"TG Assembly for Worship"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/meetings"},"Meetings"],"."],["div",{"id":"31b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.31b","order":"03.07.004.12294"},["b","31b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/2.4.2-4"},"Acts 2:4 (2–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/68.4.3-4"},"D&C 68:4 (3–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"32a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.32a","order":"03.07.004.12296"},["b","32a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/1.10.10-13"},"1 Cor. 1:10 (10–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.28.28-30"},"3 Ne. 11:28 (28–30)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/7.18"},"Moses 7:18"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/unity"},"TG Unity"],"."],["div",{"id":"32b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.32b","order":"03.07.004.12298"},["b","32b"],["span.small","GR"],"any."],["div",{"id":"32c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.32c","order":"03.07.004.12300"},["b","32c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/49.20"},"D&C 49:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"32d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.32d","order":"03.07.004.12302"},["b","32d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/consecration"},"TG Consecration"],"."],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.33a","order":"03.07.004.12304"},["b","33a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/15.15"},"1 Cor. 15:15"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/witness"},"TG Witness"],"."],["div",{"id":"33b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.33b","order":"03.07.004.12306"},["b","33b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/grace"},"TG Grace"],"."],["div",{"id":"34a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.34a","order":"03.07.004.12308"},["b","34a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/5.1.1-11"},"Acts 5:1 (1–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"35a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.35a","order":"03.07.004.12310"},["b","35a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.1"},"Acts 6:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/83.6.1-6"},"D&C 83:6 (1–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"35b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.35b","order":"03.07.004.12312"},["b","35b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/2.45"},"Acts 2:45"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/welfare"},"TG Welfare"],"."],["div",{"id":"36a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.36a","order":"03.07.004.12314"},["b","36a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/11.22.22-24"},"Acts 11:22 (22–24)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/2.1"},"Gal. 2:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"37a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.37a","order":"03.07.004.12316"},["b","37a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/19.34"},"D&C 19:34"],"."]]}
